            <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-600 p-8 text-center">
              <div class="text-6xl mb-4">üíù</div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Foster</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Without fostering, there can be no rescue. Help us save over 400 animals yearly.
              </p>
              <a href="/get-involved/foster-care" class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-700">
                Learn More
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
